import { useParams } from "react-router-dom"; import {getApplicantInfo, getJobInfo, getPredictionInfo, getAllPredictionInfo} from "../json/jsonUtil"; import { TableBody, TableCell, TableHead, TableRow, Typography } from "@material-ui/core"; import {Box} from '@material-ui/core'; import Title from "../components/Title"; export function ReturnApplicantInfo(){ let params=useParams(); let applicantID=params.applicantID; let applicantSelected=getApplicantInfo(parseInt(applicantID.substring(1,),10)); let jobSelected=getJobInfo(parseInt(applicantSelected.applicantJob)); let predictionSelected=getPredictionInfo(parseInt(applicantID.substring(1,),10),parseInt(applicantSelected.applicantJob)); let AllPredictionInfoTable=getAllPredictionInfo(applicantID.substring(1,),10); return (
{/* Selected Applicant : applicantID {applicantID} */} {/* Selected Applicant Infomation : Applicant ID : {applicantSelected.applicantID} Applicant Name : {applicantSelected.applicantName} Applicant File : {applicantSelected.applicantFile} Applicant Status : {applicantSelected.applicantStatus} Applicant Applied Job ID: {applicantSelected.applicantJob} Job Title : {jobSelected.jobTitle} Job Matching date : {jobSelected.jobMatchingDate} Job Update Date : {jobSelected.jobUpdateDate} Job Recruiter ID : {jobSelected.recruiterID} Job Hiring Manager ID : {jobSelected.hiringManagerID} Job Description : {jobSelected.jobDescription} Job Requirments : {jobSelected.jobRequirements} Prediction ID : {predictionSelected.predictionID} Prediction Result (%) : {predictionSelected.predictionResult*100} % Applicant Education Level : {predictionSelected.applicantEducation} Applicant Experience : {predictionSelected.applicantExperience} Prediction Skills : {predictionSelected.applicantSkills} */} Applicant Applied Job: {jobSelected.jobTitle} Current Reprofiled Job: {} Applicant Status: {applicantSelected.applicantStatus} Job Matching Results: Job Name % Suitability Rank in Job Applciant Job Skilles { AllPredictionInfoTable.map(each =>( {getJobInfo(each.jobID).jobTitle} {each.predictionResult} {each.Rank} {each.applicantSkills} )) }
); } export function ReturnApplicantName(){ let params=useParams(); let applicantID=params.applicantID; let applicantSelected=getApplicantInfo(parseInt(applicantID.substring(1,),10)); return applicantSelected.applicantName; }
